      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "6fc397fcafd450c3",
      "text": "Preemptive opportunities are enhanced by selecting moves that extend the period of preemptive advantage because the competitors are highly reluctant to respond to moves that dilute their strength, force them to relinquish a major commitment, or precipitate antagonistic responses from powerful vested interest groups."
